 54    a3 = softmax_apply(repmat(b3,1,numCols) + LW3_2*a2);
 55    
 56    % Output 1
 57 [Value,Recog] = max(a3);   
 58end

 61% ===== MODULE FUNCTIONS ========
 62
 63% Map Minimum and Maximum Input Processing Function
 64function y = mapminmax_apply(x,settings)
 65  y = bsxfun(@minus,x,settings.xoffset);
 66  y = bsxfun(@times,y,settings.gain);
 67  y = bsxfun(@plus,y,settings.ymin);
 68end

 69
 70% Competitive Soft Transfer Function
 71function a = softmax_apply(n,~)
 72  if isa(n,'gpuArray')
 73    a = iSoftmaxApplyGPU(n);
 74  else
 75    a = iSoftmaxApplyCPU(n);
 76  end
 77end

 78function a = iSoftmaxApplyCPU(n)
 79  nmax = max(n,[],1);
 80  n = bsxfun(@minus,n,nmax);
 81  numerator = exp(n);
 82  denominator = sum(numerator,1); 
 83  denominator(denominator == 0) = 1;
 84  a = bsxfun(@rdivide,numerator,denominator);
 85end
 86function a = iSoftmaxApplyGPU(n)
 87  nmax = max(n,[],1);
 88  numerator = arrayfun(@iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper1,n,nmax);
 89  denominator = sum(numerator,1);
 90  a = arrayfun(@iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper2,numerator,denominator);
 91end
 92function numerator = iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper1(n,nmax)
 93  numerator = exp(n - nmax);
 94end
 95function a = iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper2(numerator,denominator)
 96  if (denominator == 0)
 97    a = numerator;
 98  else
 99    a = numerator ./ denominator;
100  end
101end
102
103% Sigmoid Symmetric Transfer Function
104function a = tansig_apply(n,~)
105  a = 2 ./ (1 + exp(-2*n)) - 1;
106end
